Entry.JapaneseText: 雑貨屋「準備万端」
Entry.EnglishText: General Store

Entry.JapaneseText: おう、<Tytree>！ きょうも精が出るな！
Entry.EnglishText: Yo, waddup, <Tytree>! Let's both do our best today too!

Entry.JapaneseText: ガジュマどもを ビシビシ監督してこいよ！
Entry.EnglishText: Make sure to keep a good eye on those Gajuma!

Entry.JapaneseText: いらっしゃい！ 今日はどんな御用だい？
Entry.EnglishText: Welcome! What can I do for you?

Entry.EnglishText: Select

Entry.JapaneseText: 何だ、もう帰るのかい？ 何か買っていきなよ。
Entry.EnglishText: Oh, you're leaving? Come on, don't be shy! Buy something!

Entry.JapaneseText: 色々置いてあるから、 見てっておくれ。
Entry.EnglishText: I have all kinds of stuff here, come and take a look!

Entry.JapaneseText: またな。
Entry.EnglishText: See ya!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>、 気をつけろ！
Entry.EnglishText: You take care of yourself alright, <Tytree>?

Entry.JapaneseText: ガジュマどもは街の外に 逃げた連中を追いかけていったが、 まだ街の中に残ってるかもしれんぞ！
Entry.EnglishText: Gajumas went to go chase after those who managed to escape outside, but there might still be some left in here!

Entry.JapaneseText: 最近、ミナールへ行ったかい？ いやなにね、どうにも治安が悪くて 大変らしいんだ。
Entry.EnglishText: Ever been to Minal, lately? I heard it's become more dangerous there.

Entry.JapaneseText: ミナール経由の品物が 届かなくなったら、 困っちまうぜ……
Entry.EnglishText: It's gonna be really troublesome for me if my goods fail to get through there.

Entry.JapaneseText: な、なんだ、 この地鳴りは!?
Entry.EnglishText: Wh-Whoa!? Earthquake!

Entry.JapaneseText: いらっしゃい！ 今日はどんな御用だい？
Entry.EnglishText: Welcome! What can I do for you?

Entry.EnglishText: Select

Entry.JapaneseText: 何だ、もう帰るのかい？ 何か買っていきなよ。
Entry.EnglishText: Oh, you're leaving? Come on, don't be shy! Buy something!

Entry.JapaneseText: 色々置いてあるから、 見てっておくれ。
Entry.EnglishText: I have all kinds of stuff here, come and take a look!

Entry.JapaneseText: またな。
Entry.EnglishText: See ya!

Entry.JapaneseText: なんか工場の方で大騒ぎになってる みたいだけど商売もあるし、 抜けられないんだ。
Entry.EnglishText: Looks like there's something going on at the factory, shame I can't really leave my business over here.

Entry.JapaneseText: 見てきたら、 何があったか教えてくれよっ！
Entry.EnglishText: Let me know what's up if you go there.

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>の身に 何かがあったそうだな……
Entry.EnglishText: I heard that something happened to <Tytree>...

Entry.JapaneseText: あんたたちの しわざかい？
Entry.EnglishText: Were you the ones who did it?

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>…… 気の毒にな……
Entry.EnglishText: <Tytree>... You look like a wreck.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……元気だせよ。
Entry.EnglishText: ...Cheer up, man.

Entry.JapaneseText: セレーナが誘拐された みたいだな。
Entry.EnglishText: Looks like Selena got abducted.

Entry.JapaneseText: 一体、何が目的なんだ？ 金か？
Entry.EnglishText: Why? Did they want money? Is that it?

Entry.JapaneseText: セレーナが 助かったって？
Entry.EnglishText: So Selena's safe?

Entry.JapaneseText: そりゃよかった…… セレーナはまだ バビログラードなんだな。
Entry.EnglishText: She's still in Babilograd, huh? Thank god, she's safe...

Entry.JapaneseText: いやね、 一時はどうなるかと 思ったよ。
Entry.EnglishText: You know, at one point I wondered what would happen.

Entry.JapaneseText: 何せこの街は 事件らしい事件も ないからね。
Entry.EnglishText: After all, this town has never had an incident like that.

Entry.JapaneseText: いやあ、セレーナが助かって、 よかった、よかった……
Entry.EnglishText: Ahhh... I'm glad Selena's finally safe...

Entry.JapaneseText: いくら顔なじみの<Tytree>でも うちの商品は安くできないぜ。
Entry.EnglishText: Just coz y'all are <Tytree>'s friends, don't mean that I'll give y'all a discount, got that?

Entry.JapaneseText: こっちも生活が かかってるんだからよ。
Entry.EnglishText: My livelihood's at stake here, y'see?

Entry.JapaneseText: いつも<Tytree>が 世話になってるな。
Entry.EnglishText: Thanks for always watching over our <Tytree>.

Entry.JapaneseText: え？ 俺？ <Tytree>の従兄弟の嫁の 弟の友人さ。
Entry.EnglishText: Hm? Who am I? Oh, right, I'm <Tytree>'s cousin's wife's little brother's friend.

Entry.JapaneseText: ……実際は まったくの他人って事 だけどな。
Entry.EnglishText: But actually... I'm just a complete stranger, really.

Entry.JapaneseText: 最近、なんかガジュマが増えてさ…… 連中はみんな工場で働いてるから、 別にどうという事はないが……
Entry.EnglishText: Seems like the Gajumas have been increasing lately... Well, they're all working at the factory so no big deal...

Entry.JapaneseText: 工場の連中は色々と 大変みたいだぜ？
Entry.EnglishText: Did'ya know that the factory's in all sorts of trouble right now?

Entry.JapaneseText: もともとこの街は ガジュマが少ない街なんだ。
Entry.EnglishText: Like, before there wasn't really a lot of Gajumas in this town.

Entry.JapaneseText: それがなんでも他の街を 追い出されたとかで、 ガジュマが増えてな……
Entry.EnglishText: Now there's more coz those Gajuma got chased off from some other town or something...

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>、精が出るな！
Entry.EnglishText: Good work out there, <Tytree>!

Entry.JapaneseText: いつ帰ってくるんだ？ セレーナも心配してるぞ！
Entry.EnglishText: When're ya gonna come back, man? You're gonna make Selena worry!

Entry.JapaneseText: ここは工場の街だからな、 俺みたいな商売人は 少し肩身が狭いのさ。
Entry.EnglishText: This here's a town of factories, kinda makes a merchant like me feel a bit inferior.

Entry.JapaneseText: そういう意味では、 工場に来たガジュマも 同じかもしれないな……
Entry.EnglishText: In that sense, the Gajumas that came here must be feeling the same...

Entry.JapaneseText: 工場の奴が言ってたが、 新入りのガジュマが 不満を抱いてるんだと。
Entry.EnglishText: I heard this from someone in the factory, but apparently the new Gajumas aren't happy.

Entry.JapaneseText: まったく……新しく来たくせに 生意気な事を言う連中だ……
Entry.EnglishText: God, just because they're newcomers doesn't mean that they can go ahead and be like that...

Entry.JapaneseText: カレギア中に種族間のいがみ合いが 広がってるみたいだな。
Entry.EnglishText: It seems like the interspecies feud is spreading througout Callegea.

Entry.JapaneseText: まさかこの街でも そんな事になるとは 思わなかったよ。
Entry.EnglishText: I'd never imagine that even something like that would happen here.

Entry.JapaneseText: いやね、工場で働く ガジュマの不安が 溜まってるみたいでね。
Entry.EnglishText: Apparently the dissatisfaction between Gajumas working in the factory is slowly growing.

Entry.JapaneseText: 風のようにやって来て、 風のように去っていったあの娘……
Entry.EnglishText: Like a passing breeze, she came and left in the blink of an eye.

Entry.JapaneseText: 北の方へ向かったけど…… 今はどこにいるのやら……
Entry.EnglishText: It seemed like she was heading north... I wonder where she is now...?

Entry.JapaneseText: いつも夕方になると 家に向かう工員の姿を 見るんだけど……
Entry.EnglishText: Factory workers often pass by here around dusk...

Entry.JapaneseText: 最近、みんな浮かない顔 してるんだよな……
Entry.EnglishText: But lately, it seemed like they're depressed...

Entry.JapaneseText: あの地鳴り以来、 空気がなんとなく 変わった気がするんだ。
Entry.EnglishText: It feels like the atmosphere's changed ever since those earthquakes started happening.

Entry.JapaneseText: いや、うまくは 言えないんだけどさ、 不穏な空気が広がってるっていうか……
Entry.EnglishText: I can't really put it into words, but it's like it's gotten more restless than before.

Entry.JapaneseText: でもとりあえず、 この街は無事にやってるぜ。 なんとかな。
Entry.EnglishText: At the very least, it seems like this city's safe, I guess...

Entry.JapaneseText: オレも昔は工場で働いてたのさ。 でも、腰を痛めちまってね。 こうして商売をしてるのさ。
Entry.EnglishText: I used to work in the factory, til I broke my back, y'see. I'm just a merchant now, though.

Entry.JapaneseText: 女の子
Entry.EnglishText: Girl

Entry.JapaneseText: ああ、<Tytree>……!! ぶたないで……!!
Entry.EnglishText: Ow- <Tytree>...!! Don't hit me...!

Entry.JapaneseText: 私は南の方から逃げてきたの。 ヒューマの人に追い出されて……
Entry.EnglishText: I ran away from the south. The Humas there chased me away...

Entry.JapaneseText: ヒューマ……!! コワイよ……!!
Entry.EnglishText: Huma--! Scary...

Entry.JapaneseText: 女王様まで 処刑しようとしたなんて……
Entry.EnglishText: I heard that they tried to execute the Queen...

Entry.JapaneseText: やっぱりヒューマって 残酷なんでしょ……？
Entry.EnglishText: Humas must be really cruel, right...?

Entry.JapaneseText: ヒュー……！ ヒューマ……!!
Entry.EnglishText: H-Huma--!

Entry.JapaneseText: ほんの少しだけセレーナお姉ちゃんみたいに 優しいヒューマもいるけど、 やっぱり私はヒューマは好きになれないの……
Entry.EnglishText: It's true that there's kind Humas like Big Sis Selena, but I don't think I can really like them...

Entry.JapaneseText: だって…… コワイんだもん……
Entry.EnglishText: They scare me...

Entry.JapaneseText: きゃっ……!! ヒューマっ！
Entry.EnglishText: A-Ahhh!! A Huma!

Entry.JapaneseText: このあいだ、 来たヒューマのお姉ちゃんは とても優しかった……
Entry.EnglishText: An older Huma lady passed by, she was really kind...

Entry.JapaneseText: ヒューマにも ああいう人がいるのね……
Entry.EnglishText: So those kinds of Humas really do exist, huh...?

Entry.JapaneseText: え、えっと…… あ、あの……
Entry.EnglishText: Ah uhm... Uhh...

Entry.JapaneseText: おじちゃんは とても強そうだね。
Entry.EnglishText: Y-You look p-pretty strong, Mister.

Entry.JapaneseText: ヒューマも 怖くないんでしょ？
Entry.EnglishText: Are you also not scared of Humas?

Entry.JapaneseText: ヒューマ……!! イヤだよー！ どっか行って……!!
Entry.EnglishText: A-A H-Huma--! N-No--! Go away...!!

Entry.JapaneseText: コワイ!! 助けて!!？
Entry.EnglishText: S-Someone, save me!!

Entry.JapaneseText: ヒューマって 怖い人ばっかじゃないんだ……
Entry.EnglishText: All Humas aren't scary...

Entry.JapaneseText: でも……ヒューマの人と 話す時は体がこわばっちゃうの……
Entry.EnglishText: But... M-My body freezes up wh-whenever t-talking to one...

Entry.JapaneseText: こ、こんにちは……私…… …………
Entry.EnglishText: H-Hello... I'm...

Entry.JapaneseText: おじちゃん、 ヒューマと一緒にいて、 大丈夫なの？
Entry.EnglishText: Are you alright being with Humas, mister?

Entry.JapaneseText: 私、ヒューマは……
男の人
Entry.EnglishText: Man

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>は とても気のいい奴なんだ。
Entry.EnglishText: <Tytree>'s a really kind worker.

Entry.JapaneseText: それが…… どうしたっていうんだ、 <Tytree>のやつ……
Entry.EnglishText: But, I wonder what got to him...?

Entry.JapaneseText: 男の人
Entry.EnglishText: Man

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>はとてもいい奴だったよ…… 人を分け隔てしなかったし……
Entry.EnglishText: <Tytree> is a really good kid... He treated everyone fairly...

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>…… 俺たちはおまえの事を 忘れないぞ……
Entry.EnglishText: <Tytree>... We won't forget you...

Entry.JapaneseText: 男の人
Entry.EnglishText: Man

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>はまだ生きてるって！ こいつら、勝手に殺しやがって……
Entry.EnglishText: <Tytree>'s still alive! Those guys just decided he died...

Entry.JapaneseText: あんたら…… 助けに行ってくれるんだろ？
Entry.EnglishText: You guys came here to save him, right?

Entry.JapaneseText: 男の人
Entry.EnglishText: Man

Entry.JapaneseText: セレーナさんをかばって、 なんか一騒動あったみたいだが……
Entry.EnglishText: It seems like something happened coz he tried to protect Serena...

Entry.JapaneseText: ……まったく、最近、 世間は物騒な話ばっかだぜ。
Entry.EnglishText: Geez... the world's been filled with dangerous stuff lately.

Entry.JapaneseText: <Veigue>
Entry.EnglishText: <Veigue>

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:13000005>誰もいないな。
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:13000005>There's no one here.

Entry.JapaneseText: <Annie>
Entry.EnglishText: <Annie>

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:13000006>やっぱり……静か過ぎる……
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:13000006>Indeed, it's too quiet...

Entry.JapaneseText: <Mao>
Entry.EnglishText: <Mao>

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:13000007>見て、コレ！
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:13000007>Hey, look!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Eugene>
Entry.EnglishText: <Eugene>

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:13000008>やはり<Blue>王の盾<White>か!?
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:13000008>Could it be the <Blue>Royal Shield<White>!?

Entry.JapaneseText: <Mao>
Entry.EnglishText: <Mao>

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:13000009>あっちだよ!!
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:13000009>It's coming from over there!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Agarte>
Entry.EnglishText: <Agarte>

Entry.JapaneseText: どうしたの、<Veigue>!?
Entry.EnglishText: <Veigue>, what's wrong!?

Entry.JapaneseText: <Veigue>
Entry.EnglishText: <Veigue>

Entry.JapaneseText: ミーシャが昨日、この街で <Red>クレア<White>に会ったらしい。
Entry.EnglishText: Apparently Misha met <Red>Claire<White> here yesterday.

Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>
Entry.EnglishText: <Tytree>

Entry.JapaneseText: つまり、アガーテって事か？
Entry.EnglishText: You mean he met Agarte, right?

Entry.JapaneseText: <Veigue>
Entry.EnglishText: <Veigue>

Entry.JapaneseText: まだこの街にいるかもしれない。 アガーテが見つかれば、 クレア、おまえも元に戻れる！
Entry.EnglishText: They might still be in this town. Once we find her, we might be able to turn you back, Claire.

Entry.JapaneseText: 男の人
Entry.EnglishText: Man

Entry.JapaneseText: 男の人
Entry.EnglishText: Man

Entry.JapaneseText: 工場長
Entry.EnglishText: Manager

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:42000088>や、やったぞ……！
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:42000088>W-we did it!

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:42000089>やりましたね、工場長！
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:42000089>We put up quite a fight, didn't we Boss?

Entry.JapaneseText: 工場長
Entry.EnglishText: Manager

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:4200008a>だ、だが…… 倒しても倒してもわいて来る…… もうダメかもしれん……
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:4200008A>But it seems like no matter how many we defeat, more and more keep coming. This might not end well for us...

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:4200008b>力を合わせれば、 バイラスだって倒せるんだから、 がんばりましょうよ！
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:4200008B>These Viruses don't stand a chance as long as we work together! We can do this!

Entry.JapaneseText: セレーナ
Entry.EnglishText: Serena

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:4200008c>そうですよ、工場長！ あきらめちゃダメです！
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:4200008C>He's right, Boss! There's no need to give up!

Entry.JapaneseText: 工場長
Entry.EnglishText: Manager

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:4200008d>あ、ああ、がんばるさ……
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:4200008D>Y-yeah, okay... I'll try hanging in there...

Entry.JapaneseText: セレーナ
Entry.EnglishText: Serena

Entry.JapaneseText: <voice:4200008e><Tytree>…… あなたもがんばるのよ……
Entry.EnglishText: <voice:4200008E><Tytree>... I hope you're hanging in there, too.
